 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"977121e8525651dd0e2649e3464b636e8c769399","tid":2414111,"uid":31834,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:45:47.000Z","msg":"其實一直以來都係咁，係好撚肉鳩酸，10個有9個俾完，背後都笑鳩佢哋，當乞衣咁俾。<br />\n<br />\n真人真事<br />\n<br />\n早大約10幾年前，佢哋又係咁來收利事。但街市有檔主玩嘢，叫佢哋採青，掛到鬼撚咁高，話俾大利事。但班柒頭其實都係吸毒款，稱埋唔知有無120磅，一拳一件已經有多。<br />\n<br />\n開始採青，打邏打鼓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，開時好撚有氣勢架，成班街市佬同街坊埋嚟睇。獅尾MK想舉起前面獅頭MK，但唔知係後面唔夠力，或是前面唔識跳，就算俾佢企到上去，照睇都唔係好夠高採到。咁攪撚咗成個字都採唔到，佢哋又唔想失威，EQ 又唔係好撚高，開始燥燥地，但又唔敢發惡。氣氛開始唔對路，最後檔主打圓場，每人派封利事仔，打發佢哋走。成班街市佬，笑撚咗一年。但班柒頭之後幾年仲有來的，不過就唔行嗰條行，兜路走了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f59e577028d46c4c7960bc729998c166cee0cfb","tid":2414111,"uid":121200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9ad8420c6354690ed1e3f9e5ebea3ca0645c4f96","tid":2414111,"uid":8014,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"2021 仲黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"無辦法啦，班大種乞衣無野可以做，連黑警都做唔成咪唯有乞囉"},{"pid":"83d97e4fc9ddbeb20e5450eb6309a65b3cfad701","tid":2414111,"uid":360907,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9ad8420c6354690ed1e3f9e5ebea3ca0645c4f96","tid":2414111,"uid":8014,"like":77,"dislike":3,"score":74,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"2021 仲黑社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"2020年有政府罩<br />\n2021緊係繼續玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/goo